"description": "Retrieves a list of posts visible to the requesting user (based on authentication and relationships).\n\n- **Anonymous:** Sees only `public` posts.\n- **Authenticated:** Sees `public` posts, their own posts, `almost_private` posts from users they follow, and `private` posts they are specifically allowed to see."
},
"response": []
},
